            <title>[CAMEL-871] camel-spring - data format using camel xml elements doesnt work</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-871</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If you have a route that uses data format and you configure the data format using camel xml elements it doesn&apos;t work.&lt;/p&gt;

